languages.text: "Еще вчера я в Теневых Кварталах слонялся, на милостыню уповал, а сегодня вона как — на посту стою! Самому не верится… Слава великой Инцендии Чорда!"

traits.locale_text: [Драфт] "Еще вчера побирался под Теневыми Кварталами, а сегодня гляньте! Стою на посту! Слава Чорде!"

languages.text: "I was lurking in the Shadow Quarters and begging only yesterday, but look at me now — standing guard! Still can't believe it... Long live the great Incendia Chorda!"

languages.text: « Hier encore, je faisais la manche dans le Quartier des Ombres, et regardez-moi aujourd'hui : c'est moi qui monte la garde ! J'ai encore du mal à y croire... Longue vie à la grande Incendia Chorda ! »
languages.original_text: "I was lurking in the Shadow Quarters and begging only yesterday, but look at me now — standing guard! Still can't believe it... Long live the great Incendia Chorda!"

languages.text: “我之前还在阴影区到处乞讨，可看看现在吧！我居然成了哨兵！我真不敢相信……伟大的因森蒂娅·库尔达万岁！”
languages.original_text: "I was lurking in the Shadow Quarters and begging only yesterday, but look at me now — standing guard! Still can't believe it... Long live the great Incendia Chorda!"

traits.locale_text: “我之前还在阴影区到处乞讨，可看看现在的我！我居然成了哨兵！我真不敢相信……伟大的因森蒂娅·库尔达万岁！”

languages.text: "Erst gestern habe ich mich noch in den Schattenquartieren versteckt und gebettelt, und seht mich jetzt an – ich halte Wache! Ich kann's immer noch nicht glauben ... Lang lebe die große Incendia Chorda!"
languages.original_text: "I was lurking in the Shadow Quarters and begging only yesterday, but look at me now — standing guard! Still can't believe it... Long live the great Incendia Chorda!"

languages.text: «Ayer me escondía en los barrios bajos, mendigando, y mírame ahora, ¡soy guardia! Todavía no me lo creo... ¡Larga vida a la gran Incendia Chorda!».
languages.original_text: "I was lurking in the Shadow Quarters and begging only yesterday, but look at me now — standing guard! Still can't believe it... Long live the great Incendia Chorda!"

traits.locale_text: «Ayer me escondía en los barrios bajos, y mírame ahora, ¡estoy de guardia! Todavía no me lo creo... ¡Larga vida a la gran Incendia Chorda!».

languages.text: "Daha dün Gölge Mahalli'nin kuytu köşelerinde sürünüp yalvarıyordum. Bir de şu anki hâlime bakın! Nöbet tutuyorum! Hâlâ inanamıyorum... Muhteşem İncendia Chorda çok yaşa!"
languages.original_text: "I was lurking in the Shadow Quarters and begging only yesterday, but look at me now — standing guard! Still can't believe it... Long live the great Incendia Chorda!"

traits.locale_text: "Daha dün gibi… Gölge Mahali'nin kuytu köşelerinde sürünüp yalvarıyordum. Şu anki hâlime bir bakın! Nöbet tutuyorum! Hâlâ inanamıyorum… Çok yaşa muhteşem İncendia Chorda!"
